      "content": "okay but you keep saying it's a \"clear violation of international law.\" aren't the specific maritime boundaries and the validity of the UNCLOS rulings actually a huge point of debate among legal scholars? it seems like you're presenting the Western legal interpretation as the only absolute truth rather than one side of a legal argument.",
